Focus Indicators
All interactive elements must have:

Visible focus ring (ring-2)
Color change on focus
Outline removed (focus:outline-none)
Color Independence
Never rely on color alone for information:

Use icons with status colors
Provide text labels
Add borders for emphasis
💡 Design Principles (Enterprise Grade)
Professional Depth: Use sophisticated grays with indigo/purple accents
Glassmorphism: Backdrop blur with strategic opacity for modern depth
Subtle Gradients: Text and backgrounds use refined gradients
Consistent Shadows: Layered shadows with glows for premium feel
Icon Containers: Background containers for visual hierarchy
Border Emphasis: Subtle borders that glow on interaction
Status Clarity: Icons + text + color for all status indicators
Smooth Interactions: 200ms transitions with scale and glow effects
Typography Hierarchy: Gradient text for stats and emphasis
Professional Polish: Every detail refined for enterprise quality
