🚀 Implementation Guidelines
CSS Framework
Tailwind CSS v3.3+ with custom configuration

Key Technical Decisions
Backdrop blur for all glass surfaces
Strategic use of opacity (40-80%)
Gradient text for statistics
Icon containers for visual weight
Border emphasis over heavy shadows
Subtle scale transforms (102-105%)
Performance Optimization
Use transform for animations (GPU)
Minimize backdrop-blur usage on mobile
Lazy load images and icons
Optimize gradient rendering
Use CSS containment where applicable
Browser Support
Modern browsers (2020+)
CSS backdrop-filter support required
Fallback: solid backgrounds for older browsers
